data.description: Meticulously maintained Mid-Century Modern home on 1.65 acres. 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath with living AND family rooms, jetted tub in guest bath, all on one level! Living room has vaulted ceilings and huge windows to take in the view of the manicured yard. Huge primary suite with large walk-in closet. Multiple out-buildings including 36 X 36 shop, extra deep 2-car garage, 2-car carport with storage buildings and RV covered parking. 1.78 acre neighboring lot also for sale separately.
